# Why I Feed One AI’s Output Into Another (and Why You Should Too).
In my use of AI, I have found that disagreeing with AI is the best way to get to the truth. 
Sometimes the AI will hallucinate and claim that something is the truth and the only correct
answer. We want to disagree with the claims of AI and get to the actual truth and best
implementations. To do this, I copy the output from one AI and feed it to another AI. That
may be the same model in a different chat or using a completely different AI altogether.
